Instalation creates a .cc_notebook.ini file in your home directory fill out the relevant sections

To enable jsmol the jsmol directory needs to be copied to the cc_notebook/static  directory

Download the latest jmol binary tar.gz file (http://sourceforge.net/projects/jmol/)
From Jmol-x-binary.tar.gz navigate to the jmol directory and extract jsmol.zip file
From the extracted jsmol.zip extract the jsmol directory 
copy/move the jsmol directory to the cc_notebook/static  directory


